title: 15 MIN DEEP FULL BODY STRETCH - Improve Mobility & Flexibility - Daily stretch to help you recover
description:
A follow-along Deep Full Body Stretch from beautiful Greece! Take 15 minutes to help your body recover and feel better. I promise your body will thank you after finishing this quick & effective mobility session ♡ 

▸ Focus: Recovery & Mobility
▸ Time: 15 Minutes
▸ No Equipment
▸ 50 sec on, 10 sec off to change to the next stretch 

Please remember that we are all different and that you can make this your own workout ♡ Take a longer break when you need to.
